#################################################
#						#
#		Scripts description		#
#						#
# tree - each file creates based on previus work#
# We mark it as a tree and branches. for example#
# file '1.1' depend on valid run of file '1'    #
#################################################

tree	file	description
0	file_dependencies.R	Enable run all files one by one
1	FeatureTable_not_filtered.R		Create copy of QIIME2 results
1	metadata_not_filtered.R		Create copy of metadata
1.1	FinalSetOfSamples.R		Create list of sample that pass our criteria	  
1.1.1     metadata.R	Create metadata file
1.1.2     FeatureTable.R	Create Table of features 
1.1.1.1       OneSamplePerKidPerTimePoint.R	Choose set with only one sample per kid in each time point 
1.1.1.1.1.1             DiversityOutput.R	Calculate diversity matrix between all samples
1.1.1.1.1.1.1                 RichnessOverall.R		Calculate Richness overall samples
1.1.1.1.1.1.1.1                 CompositionPlotOverall_MY_line.R	Plot the composition
1.1.1.1             Figure1Numbers.R	Calculate numbers for Figure 1A
1.1.1.2		venn.R		Plot a venn diagram of of all samples crossed by filter criteria
1.1.1.3             SampleMapSubsets.R		Figure 1 sample map
1.1.1.4       SubsetsLists.R	Create all subsets list of samples
1.1.1.4.1         MaAsLin2.R	Run maaslin on each subset and each chosen model
1.1.1.4.1.1           SuppTable1.R	Supplementary table (all maaslin output)
1.1.1.4.1.1.1             AppRdata.R 
1.1.1.4.1.1.1.1               AppFunc.R 
1.1.1.4.1.1.1.1.1                 AppDeploy.R 
1.1.1.4.1.1.2             BoxPlotVagBacteroides.R	Plot
1.1.1.4.1.1.3             BoxPlotDietBifido.R	Plot
1.1.1.4.1.1.4             BoxPlotProLacto.R	Plot
1.1.1.4.1.1.5             FlagPostCases0.01.R	Plot
1.1.1.4.1.1.6             FlagPostSymp0.01.R	Plot
1.1.1.4.1.1.7             FlagPostCases0.025.R	Plot
1.1.1.4.1.1.8             FlagPostSymp0.025.R	Plot
1.1.1.4.1.1.9             FlagPostCases0.05.R	Plot
1.1.1.4.1.1.10             FlagPostSymp0.05.R	Plot
